# Spark Animation Assets

This directory will contain:
- Static SVG files (idle-curious.svg with eye-tracking)
- APNG animation files (multi-frame expressions)
- Reaction animations (click/drag responses)
- Mini mode animations (screen-edge peeking)

See ANIMATION_GUIDE.md for frame creation instructions.

Current status:
✅ SVG templates created (idle, happy, thinking, tired, dizzy, playful, sleeping, concerned)
⏳ APNG animations pending (convert SVGs to multi-frame animations)
